1)Create Project: File -> New -> Project-> Select maven -> click next

2)Name: batch81Cucumber->finish

3)Add Dependencies =>Selenium-java, webdrivermanager,
 cucumber java, cucumber junit

4)Click Maven => click “Enable auto-reload after any changes”
(BU MESAJ GORUNMEYEDEBILIR)

5)Java’ya sag click yapip asagidaki paketleri olusturalim
-utilities
-pages
-runners (test case’leri calistirmak ve control etmek icin kullanacagiz)
-stepdefinitions (kodlarimizi burada olusturacagiz)

